        "subject": "LU-5984 obd: fix lastid file name in compat code",
        "message": "LU-5984 obd: fix lastid file name in compat code\n\nThe lastid_compat_check() tries to find last_id file from\npre-2.4 Lustre with wrong name, so lastid counter in the new\nLASTID file is initialized with wrong value. This causes FID\nre-use and inability to create new files in given sequence.\n\nPatch contains also fix for possibly damaged filesystem, it\nreads old lastid file always to check if it contains bigger\nlastid value.\n\nSigned-off-by: Mikhail Pershin <mike.pershin@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I482331bb0d6d5a286d94d56b943cbff2a82ac37f\n"
      },
